https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lam0cYOEst8

npx create-mf-app
  api-server
  API Server
  8080
  express
npx create-mf-app
  client
  Application
  3000
  react
  typescript
  Tailwind
yarn in package directory
cd api-server
  yarn
  npx tsc --init
  yarn add @trpc/server zod cors
  yarn add @types/cors -D
cd client
  yarn
  yarn add @trpc/client @trpc/react react-query zod
  npx tsc --init

Connect Client to the server:
  cd client
  yarn add <server-name>@<server-version> from server's package.json
  yarn add api-server@1.0.0



start apps:
  cd api-server
    yarn start
  cd client
    yarn start

